OL,3,CMerseyside Police stop motorist
OL,4,Cdriving 'Ace Ventura' style in snow-
OL,5,Ccovered car
OL,7,FMerseyside Police officers have
OL,8,Fstopped a motorist as he drove his
OL,9,Fsnow-covered car by hanging out of the
OL,10,Fwindow 'Ace Ventura' style.
OL,12,FThe car's windscreen was totally
OL,13,Fcovered by snow and ice when officer's
OL,14,Fspotted it, calling the driver's
OL,15,Fbehaviour "simply not acceptable".
OL,17,FPosting the image on social media they
OL,18,Fcaptioned it, "Just when you think you
OL,19,Fhave seen it all!
