OL,3,CMerseyside Police stop motorist
OL,4,Cdriving 'Ace Ventura' style in snow-
OL,5,Ccovered car
OL,7,F"This vehicle was being driven exactly
OL,8,Fas you see it in the picture with the
OL,9,Fdriver hanging out of the window Ace
OL,10,FVentura-style.
OL,12,F"We didn't think we needed to say it,
OL,13,Fbut that is simply not acceptable and
OL,14,Fthe driver has been reported."
OL,16,FIn the 1994 film Ace Ventura: Pet
OL,17,FDetective, actor Jim Carrey's
OL,18,Fcharacter drives a car with his head
OL,19,Fout of the window because the
OL,20,Fwindscreen was smashed.
