OL,7,FAA president Edmund King says, "We
OL,8,Fhave previously warned of dangerous
OL,9,F'tank commander' drivers who just
OL,10,Fscrape a small hole on the windscreen
OL,11,Fto peer out, but this example is a
OL,12,Fmuch more kamikaze approach as the
OL,13,Fdriver won't see a thing.
OL,15,F"It only takes 10 minutes maximum to
OL,16,Fscrape a windscreen.
OL,18,F"Or you can get an electric vehicle
OL,19,Fwhich can be preconditioned to defrost
OL,20,Fthe car."
