OL,7,FUnder the Road Traffic Act 1988,
OL,8,Fdrivers must have a "full view of the
OL,9,Froad and traffic ahead".
OL,11,FFailing to remove snow properly from a
OL,12,Fwindscreen could result in a #60 fine
OL,13,Fand three penalty points.
OL,15,FAs the weather has become increasingly
OL,16,Fsevere Merseyside Police urged drivers
OL,17,Fto "take extra care" in wintry
OL,18,Fconditions.
